    "problemStatement": "### **Aptitude Practice Question**\n\nShe _____ the book from the library yesterday.\u00a0\n\nA. Borrowed\nB. lent\nC. Bought\u00a0\nD. Gave\u00a0\n\n---\n\n### **Answer & Explanation**\n\nA\u00a0Explanation: \n\n\"Borrowed\" means to take something temporarily, such as a book from the library.",
